18:25.291 --> 18:27.000
- Please.
- Okay.

18:27.000 --> 18:28.917
- Okay.
- All right.

18:28.917 --> 18:30.417
You ready for this?

18:30.417 --> 18:31.834
Yes, I am a strong woman.

18:31.834 --> 18:34.333
All right,
let's see here.

18:34.333 --> 18:36.917
Hmm, well,
for beginners,

18:36.917 --> 18:39.000
