to recognize that
all of this bullshit

19:49.583 --> 19:53.208
comes from a very deep,
dank, dark, toxic well
of insecurity,

19:53.208 --> 19:55.166
probably created
by your absent father.

19:55.166 --> 19:58.125
And that allows you to be
a sympathetic character.

19:59.250 --> 20:01.291
